name: Repetitive Process - Print Edition #1
description:
This project is based on the repetitive action of riding a bike and screen printing. I have developed an alternate method of registering the paper while printing. By keeping the screen in a fixed position and moving the paper at different angles from a central point when registering the image, overlay builds up and creates these patterns within the printed image.

Screen printed with water based inks onto GF Smith Colorplan Cool Grey 175gsm, 500 x 500 mm.

All posters stamped on the back, signed and numbered /20.

For more images and information about the project please refer to my website and blog.

For any international orders please email - info@dnylne.com

Thanks!

End of summer SALE!
